{
  "stem": "893.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as-- to them, I spoke perfectly Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they had no-- no way of detecting that I'm not telling the truth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my father's Slovakian was very poor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He grew up as-- he grew up in a family where they spoke German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And on the street, I guess, he picked up Hungarian, or, probably, his schooling was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother came from a small town-- from a small village in Slovakia, so she spoke.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't-- her Slovakian wasn't the literary Slovakian.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Her Slovakian was the-- was sort of Slovakian that was spoken in that region.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't the literary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But she spoke that well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She spoke well Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she also spoke German, and Yiddish, I guess.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Her parents-- in her house, they spoke Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My grandmother came from Poland, just across the border-- well, at that time there were no borders between that part of Slovakia and Galicia, because all that belonged to the Hungary and Austrian Empire.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's September of '44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- through the grapevine, we found out that the Hungarians were upset that, I guess, the world opinion or-- or the Western countries, heard about the Auschwitz-- about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- they threatened that the people will be brought to justice, who are doing-- perpetrators of the-- of that-- of these horrible things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the Hungarian government, or the Hungarian-- sort of the president of Hungary, or the-- he was regent, because Hungary was supposed to be a kingdom, and they didn't have a king.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the head of the state was called the regent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name was Horthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he decided-- he wanted, actually, to get out of the-- out of the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans were-- and so he formed a military government.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
